    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>In Tmes Of Madness</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>In times of madness </l>
          <l>in times of war </l>
          <l>we are sitting so quietly </l>
          <l>and waiting for more </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>What have we done to you </l>
          <l>i really don't know </l>
          <l>Pease pass me the bread my friend </l>
          <l>cause the soup is getting cold </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>In times of separation </l>
          <l>in times of supremacy </l>
          <l>We are living in silence </l>
          <l>and waiting to be judged </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>What have we done to you </l>
          <l>i really don't know </l>
          <l>Please pass me the soap my child </l>
          <l>cause the shower is getting tox </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Megalomanias </l>
          <l>so vicious and mean </l>
          <l>Will they still have their mega power </l>
          <l>without their thing</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
